-- Deutsche Bank Names Lampard Head of Global Markets for Its Canadian Region
-- David Scanlan
-- 2010-07-21T14:37:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-21/deutsche-bank-names-lampard-head-of-global-markets-for-its-canadian-region.html

          
          
             Deutsche Bank said it hired Scott
Lampard as head of global markets for Canada. Lampard, formerly
at Bank of America Merrill Lynch, will be based in Toronto.  
          
          


  


        